author: tobrien
msg: Fixed the maven site generation.  Commons Maven sites are generated from jakarta-commons/<project> directories, and ../incl_nav.xml references jakarta-commons/incl_nav.xml.  If we try to reference ../../incl_nav.xml then 'maven site:generate' will spit out a no such file or directory.
